RACE.RACE_TEXT: Clever Trevor S. REMINGTON PARK RACE 8 7F Dirt CR: 86. Stakes Purse 75000. FOR TWO YEAR OLDS. No nomination fee, $750 to pass the entry box. Starters to pay $750 additional with $75,000 guaranteed. Supplementary nominations may be made at time of entry for a fee of $3,000, which qualifies to start. Starters to be named through t he entry box by the usual time of closing. Weights: 121 lbs. Non-winners of a sweepstakes allowed 2 lbs., Non Winners of a race other than maiden or claiming 4 lbs., maidens 6 lbs. High weights on a scale preferred. Total earnings will be used in determ ining the order of preference of horses with equal weights on the scale. Earnings will be determined according to statistics provided by Equibase. This race will be limited to 12 starters. The guaranteed money to be divided 60% to the winner, 20% to secon d, 11% to third, 6% to fourth and 3% to fifth. A suitable award will be presented to the winning owner.
